#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:2
msgid "lmcache describe"
msgstr "lmcache 描述"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:4
msgid ""
"The ``lmcache describe`` command shows the detailed status of a running "
"LMCache service, including cache health, L1 storage, registered models, "
"and L2 adapters."
msgstr ""
"``lmcache describe`` 命令显示正在运行的 LMCache 服务的详细状态，包括缓存健康状况、L1 存储、注册的模型和 L2 "
"适配器。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:50
msgid "The output shows:"
msgstr "输出显示："

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:52
msgid "**Overview** — health status, engine type, chunk size."
msgstr "**概述** — 健康状态、引擎类型、块大小。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:53
msgid "**L1 storage** — capacity, usage, eviction policy, cached object count."
msgstr "**L1 存储** — 容量、使用情况、逐出策略、缓存对象数量。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Registered models** — per-model KV cache layout: a context-wide summary"
" followed by one kernel group section per kernel group, each with the GPU"
" KV tensor shape (symbolic and concrete), attention backend, and group "
"geometry."
msgstr "**注册模型** — 每个模型的 KV Cache 布局：一个上下文范围的摘要，后面跟着每个内核组的一个内核组部分，每个部分都有 GPU KV 张量形状（符号和具体）、注意力后端和组几何。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:57
msgid "**L2 adapters** — type, health, backend, stored objects, and utilization."
msgstr "**L2 适配器** — 类型、健康状况、后端、存储对象和利用率。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:60
msgid "Options"
msgstr "选项"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:66
msgid "Flag"
msgstr "标志"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:67
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:68
msgid "``kvcache``"
msgstr "``kvcache``"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:69
msgid ""
"Target to describe (positional, required; currently only ``kvcache`` is "
"supported)."
msgstr "描述目标（位置参数，必需；当前仅支持 ``kvcache``）。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:71
msgid "``--url``"
msgstr "``--url``"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:72
msgid "LMCache HTTP server URL (default: ``http://localhost:8080``)."
msgstr "LMCache HTTP 服务器 URL（默认：``http://localhost:8080``）。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:73
msgid "``--format``"
msgstr "``--format``"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:74
msgid "Output format: ``terminal`` (default) or ``json``."
msgstr "输出格式：``terminal``（默认）或``json``。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:75
msgid "``--output PATH``"
msgstr "``--output PATH``"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:76
msgid "Save metrics to a file (format follows ``--format``)."
msgstr "将指标保存到文件中（格式遵循 ``--format``）。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:77
msgid "``-q`` / ``--quiet``"
msgstr "``-q`` / ``--quiet``"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:78
msgid "Suppress stdout output. Exit code only."
msgstr "抑制标准输出。仅返回退出代码。"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:81
msgid "JSON Output"
msgstr "JSON 输出"

#: ../../source/cli/describe.rst:83
msgid ""
"Use ``--format json`` for machine-readable output. Models, kernel groups,"
" and L2 adapters are collected into lists for easy programmatic access:"
msgstr "使用 ``--format json`` 以机器可读的输出格式。模型、内核组和 L2 适配器被收集到列表中，以便于程序化访问："

